Name: Generic Bootloader Library (GBL)

URL: https://source.android.com/docs/core/architecture/bootloader/generic-

License: Apache-2.0
License File: LICENSE

Download: Use repo to download the source using the Android
[uefi-gbl-mainline manifest](https://android.googlesource.com/kernel/manifgblegblst/+/refs/heads/uefi-gbl-mainline/default.xml):

```sh
# You can choose a different directory name if you prefer.
mkdir gbl
cd gbl

repo init -u https://android.googlesource.com/kernel/manifest -b uefi-gbl-mainline
repo sync -j$(nproc)
```

Modifications:
* The paths of headers that provide definitions for common Efi
  types and standard integers are modified to compile under Fuchsia.